@startuml legend
title Legend — Symbol Vocabulary
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor white
skinparam ArrowColor #111
skinparam ArrowFontColor #111

skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam card {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}

actor "Human user" as HumanUser
actor "Agent\n(Claude, etc.)" as Agent #LightSkyBlue

card "Skill /\nslash command" as Skill #LightYellow
rectangle "External input\n(observation,\nuser intent,\nfailing test)" as Input #FFFFFF;line.dashed
database "Persistent\nstore" as Store
usecase "Decision\npoint" as Decision
rectangle "Action /\nside effect" as Action #LightGreen;line.dashed
rectangle "Convention /\nartifact\n(file in repo)" as Convention #Lavender

note bottom of HumanUser : Stick figure, white background — the project maintainer or contributor invoking workflows directly.
note bottom of Agent : Stick figure, light blue background — an AI agent (Claude Code, Codex CLI, etc.) acting on user's behalf. Distinguished from human by background color.
note bottom of Skill : Yellow card — a slash command exposed by livespec-core or an implementation plugin (e.g., /livespec:revise, /livespec-impl-*:capture-spec-gaps).
note bottom of Input : Dashed rectangle, white background — something outside the workflow surface that flows in (an observation, a memo's source thought, a CI failure).
note bottom of Store : Cylinder — a persistent data store (SPECIFICATION/, .beads/, repo files, work-item queue).
note bottom of Decision : Oval — a branch point that routes based on a condition or user choice.
note bottom of Action : Green dashed rectangle — an action taken inside a workflow (writing a file, running a check, computing a diff).
note bottom of Convention : Lavender rectangle — a structured artifact written by a workflow to the repo (e.g., .ai/<topic>.md, AGENTS.md reference).

@enduml
